<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-14-0801 </DOCNO><TEXT>Direct energy consumption by households, accounts for over one quarterof the overall national energy consumption. The aims of Finland's energypolicy are, quaranteed energy supply, the economical use of energy andself-sufficiency of energy supply. To achieve these aims, where householdsare concerned, attempts have been made to influence them primarily throughincreased information but partly also by grants and building regulations.</TEXT></DOC>